These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-1::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: magic-tricks, writing, singing, chess
The people have 4 different jobs:  coach, police-officer, journalist, teacher
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: jazz, classical, dubstep, soul
4 different pets are kept: rat, chinchilla, goat, turtle
1. the police-officer is the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
2. the fan of soul is on the left of the owner of the chinchilla##1
3. the fan of dubstep is the coach##1
4. the person who's hobby is chess is on the right of the police-officer##1
5. the journalist is on the right of the person who's hobby is writing##1
6. the fan of jazz is on the left of the fan of classical##1
7. the police-officer is the owner of the rat##1
8. the fan of classical is on the right of the owner of the goat##1
9. the person who's hobby is chess is on the left of the owner of the goat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Hobby         | magic-tricks  | chess  | writing | singing |
| Job           | police-officer | coach | teacher  | journalist  |
| Music-Genre   | soul       | dubstep      | jazz | classical      |
| Pet           | rat          | chinchilla     | goat    | turtle     |

