.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: water, soy-milk, fanta, hot-chocolate
There 4 different types of food: raspberry, cucumber, peach, pomegranate
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: metal, country, r&b, blues
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: surfing, biathlon, climbing, badminton
1. the person eating raspberry is on the far right##1
2. the fan of blues is the person who's sport is surfing##1
3. the person eating peach is on the right of the person drinking water##1
4. the person who's sport is climbing is on the left of the person eating cucumber##1
5. the fan of blues is on the left of the fan of metal##1
6. the person drinking fanta is the fan of r&b##1
7. the fan of country is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1
8. the person who's sport is climbing is on the left of the person drinking water##1
9. the person who's sport is surfing is on the right of the person who's sport is badminton##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |    3     |     4      |
| Beverage      | fanta     | water       | soy-milk | hot-chocolate        |
| Food          | pomegranate     | cucumber       | peach   | raspberry   |
| Music-Genre   | r&b      | country       | blues     | metal    |
| Sport         | climbing | badminton | surfing | biathlon |

