.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-3::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: sprite, cola, iced-tea, lemonade
The people have 4 different jobs:  photographer, entrepreneur, teacher, paramedic
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: spy, epic, superhero, comedy
4 different pets are kept: rat, turtle, guinea-pig, fish
 1. the person drinking lemonade is the owner of the fish##1
 2. the person drinking iced-tea is on the far right##1
 3. the person watching superhero movies is on the far right##1
 4. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left of the owner of the rat##1
 5. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the person watching spy movies##1
 6. the person watching spy movies is on the left of the person watching epic movies##1
 7. the person watching epic movies is on the right of the entrepreneur##1
 8. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the photographer##1
 9. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the owner of the fish##1
10. the person drinking iced-tea is the paramedic##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |     3      |       4        |
| Beverage      | cola | sprite       | lemonade        | iced-tea        |
| Job           | entrepreneur   | teacher | photographer   | paramedic |
| Movie-Genre   | spy     | epic    | comedy | superhero        |
| Pet           | guinea-pig         | rat  | fish       | turtle         |

