3. the fan of house is on the far right##1
4. the writer is on the left of the owner of the lizard##1
5. the fan of house is on the right of the fan of indie##1
6. the fan of trance is on the right of the dressmaker##1
7. the writer is on the right of the photographer##1
8. the canadian is on the far right##1
9. the owner of the dog is the pakistani##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |     3     |      4      |
