.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-5::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  software-developer, chef, paramedic, project-manager
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: thriller, comedy, musical, animation
There are 4 different nationalities: malaysian, chinese, canadian, japanese
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: tennis, volleyball, swimming, golf
1. the person watching musical movies is on the far left##1
2. the person who's sport is tennis is on the right of the software-developer##1
3. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the far left##1
4. the chinese is on the left of the malaysian##1
5. the japanese is on the right of the person who's sport is golf##1
6. the person who's sport is golf is the canadian##1
7. the malaysian is on the left of the person watching thriller movies##1
8. the chef is on the right of the person watching comedy movies##1
9. the person watching thriller movies is on the right of the paramedic##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |       3       |      4       |
| Job           | software-developer  | paramedic    | chef | project-manager |
| Movie-Genre   | musical      | comedy    | thriller         | animation    |
| Nationality   | chinese   | malaysian     | canadian          | japanese      |
| Sport         | volleyball | tennis | golf      | swimming      |

