.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-7::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, water, almond-milk, sprite
The people have 4 different hobbies: magic-tricks, hiking, skydiving, camping
4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, horse, snake, mouse
The people use 4 different means of transport: bus, ship, trike, car
 1. the owner of the chinchilla is the person who's hobby is hiking##1
 2. the person driving the car is on the left of the person drinking water##1
 3. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
 4. the owner of the horse is on the left of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
 5. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the right of the owner of the mouse##1
 6. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the left of the person who's hobby is camping##1
 7. the owner of the chinchilla is the person driving the trike##1
 8. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the far left##1
 9. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the person drinking water##1
10. the person driving the bus is on the left of the person driving the trike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Beverage    | hot-chocolate | water     | almond-milk    | sprite |
| Hobby       | magic-tricks | skydiving    | camping | hiking |
| Pet         | horse   | snake  | mouse        | chinchilla    |
| Transport   | car   | ship | bus    | trike |

