5. the person driving the taxi is on the left of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
6. the person driving the jet-ski is the person who's hobby is fishing##1
7. the person driving the skateboard is the owner of the turtle##1
8. the fan of techno is on the far left##1
9. the fan of pop is the person who's hobby is fishing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |      3      |     4      |
