6. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the left of the person who's sport is basketball##1
7. the russian is on the right of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
8. the person who's hobby is collecting is the person drinking iced-tea##1
9. the turkish is on the right of the person who's sport is rugby##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |       2       |    3     |      4      |
| Beverage      | sprite     | iced-tea           | 7up    | water    |
| Hobby         | skydiving  | collecting | filmmaking  | singing |
