5. the person driving the bike is on the left of the person driving the roller##1
6. the fan of r&b is on the left of the person eating apple##1
7. the person driving the trike is on the left of the person driving the quad-bike##1
8. the person eating apple is on the far right##1
9. the australian is on the left of the fan of indie##1

